UIC Alumni Association


Alumni Career Services






Alumni Career Services
Earning your degree at UIC is just one step on your career journey and the UIC Alumni Association is here to help you to find success after your degree. Whether you’re trying to land your first job, make a career transition, build a network or looking to share the secrets of your success with others, the UICAA has resources and opportunities to enrich your professional life.





